lyrics:
Pathian mite u Pathian mite u,
A thu puang rawh u;
A hming mak tak chu, Ram tinah hril r'u;
Thil zawng zawng ngamtu leh Chhandamtu a ni;
Ram zawng zawng Lalber leh Khawvel awptu chu.
Lal ropui ber chu, Min tlantu a ni;
Anin min hruai a, Ahmaah kan awm;
Mi zawng zawngin sa r'u, A hla mawi ber chu;
Isua min Chhandamtu, Amah fak fovin.
Chhandamna Pathian, Khawvel siamtu chu;
Mi zawng zawng auvin, A Fapa fa r'u;
Angel-ho zawng pawhin, Amah an fak a;
A hmaa kum theuhvin, Chibai an buk thin.
Tunah hlim takin, Amah fak theuh r'u;
Thil ropui ber pawh Amahin a siam;
Mi zawng zawngin tunah Zah theuh tawh ula;
Amah chawimawi fo r'u, Chatuan thleng pawhin.
